  "detailed_description": "<br><br><strong>Be vigilant against card counters, cheaters, and, of course, thieves. When you can't keep up, you may need to hire a few people to ensure security.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711070/extras/10fddb0b4ce7cb0f978775f8d9490362.poster.avif?t=1772624753\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711070/extras/10fddb0b4ce7cb0f978775f8d9490362.webm?t=1772624753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711070/extras/10fddb0b4ce7cb0f978775f8d9490362.mp4?t=1772624753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Design your casino as you wish. Impress your guests with luxurious decoration, colorful lights, and elegant furniture. Create an atmosphere filled with table games and slot machines. Also, don't forget to provide an unforgettable experience in specially arranged rooms for VIPs!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711070/extras/aca27b9c8e1aec830ab9b76a5332bcca.poster.avif?t=1772624753\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711070/extras/aca27b9c8e1aec830ab9b76a5332bcca.webm?t=1772624753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711070/extras/aca27b9c8e1aec830ab9b76a5332bcca.mp4?t=1772624753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Machines and tables set for cheating and low winnings promise high profits; however, every advantage comes with a disadvantage. Games managed with this tactic are low-profile and attract fewer customers. Find the balance, take risks, and elevate your casino to the top.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711070/extras/51dddfb938cb04294017bad4467e040e.poster.avif?t=1772624753\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711070/extras/51dddfb938cb04294017bad4467e040e.webm?t=1772624753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711070/extras/51dddfb938cb04294017bad4467e040e.mp4?t=1772624753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Shall we see if luck is on your side? Because sometimes, a single roll of the dice or a single number can bring in more than days of hard work in your job.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711070/extras/2f9cec7bafceb7fcbd029f8076d33635.poster.avif?t=1772624753\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711070/extras/2f9cec7bafceb7fcbd029f8076d33635.webm?t=1772624753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711070/extras/2f9cec7bafceb7fcbd029f8076d33635.mp4?t=1772624753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Don't Forget to Have Fun.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711070/extras/0cdf933457e061b206062fb68f2f108d.poster.avif?t=1772624753\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711070/extras/0cdf933457e061b206062fb68f2f108d.webm?t=1772624753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steam